If you want to delete your gym or fitness place data , you have to send email from your registered email address that you want to delete all data of your gym

Below data will be deleted
Members Profile Data
Members Payment Data 
Members Attendance Data 

Its important that you mention your 'Gym ID' that you can find in /more > Team Management Page

Once data is deleted we wont be able to recover it.

You can also request to delete your account.

